{"tid":1391953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如一齊睇下委內瑞拉人點示威","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:20:24.000Z","uid":64781,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0208fa0d6e9c28c064ae458723dd32757ed5f33a","tid":1391953,"uid":64781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"講少少背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n委內瑞拉示威是發生在<span style=\"color: gold;\">2014年至今</span>，委內瑞拉一系列的政治示威抗議活動，反對總統尼古拉斯&middot;馬杜羅領導的執政黨委內瑞拉統一社會主義黨政府。抗議活動理由包括高暴力犯罪率、基本物資不足<br />\n<br />\n用雞尾酒停止防暴車衝向市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G40NYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G40NYq.png&h=716f66e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阻止暴徒攻擊市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/ZaKkpRSUuBBR9gU3Hz/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FZaKkpRSUuBBR9gU3Hz%2Fgiphy.gif&h=aec2abd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較溫和既方法對付<span style=\"color: gold;\">列陣既暴徒</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/TJO6AdxtyXfILHOkaU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FTJO6AdxtyXfILHOkaU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=76db7b8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bcb558e3bafa932c517111b217f72b7a4bda325","tid":1391953,"uid":64781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d10f2c8c2a59003763920de6ca3a3e94a3fccd","tid":1391953,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcb558e3bafa932c517111b217f72b7a4bda325","tid":1391953,"uid":64781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"